{"tid":9862,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[本地籃球] 有冇人留意開香港本地甲組籃球？","createTime":"2016-11-28T17:26:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T15:15:42.000Z","uid":18526,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cfeae109d30d9b73f25caaee6601abbd92fb5b93","tid":9862,"uid":18526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:26:39.000Z","msg":"香港本地甲組籃球賽，今年都幾有觀賞性，又有埋ABL，主場作客咁打，具職業規模。<br />\n<br />\n加上南華，永倫，東方，飛鷹等均有外援幫手，有冇巴打有睇開？可以討論吓！<br />\n<br />\n雖然銀牌聯賽未正式開波，但睇咗頭場ABL(頭2節only)，東方隊實力都幾強，內外夾攻，今年又有冇望衝擊到聯賽冠軍呢？"},{"pid":"672d4286c9940fd367de41a7df596a44a3051775","tid":9862,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:28:50.000Z","msg":"召喚Joel巴打"},{"pid":"eb5f46cce319f2ee4d1ebd998839f48125f4d1e6","tid":9862,"uid":269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:23:43.000Z","msg":"咪又係幾隊班霸玩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce12f6c14d7bd3b5047f1200339b4fa4f4c1a928","tid":9862,"uid":29284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:06:14.000Z","msg":"有冇人有睇前幾日東方 最尾1分幾鐘輸緊十分到最後奇蹟反勝 好熱血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b98ac509c77f3219aa174fd4a6035bb5f0f74f","tid":9862,"uid":32340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:11:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人有睇前幾日東方 最尾1分幾鐘輸緊十分到最後奇蹟反勝 好熱血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n李琪同siu wing 都各入一球三分， 把握力幾好"},{"pid":"fb94a05580170bb7ea64dd66048d80e24debfc37","tid":9862,"uid":965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T08:54:50.000Z","msg":"陳兆榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa64ac13031d8a89a87d7fabe3872c1ae271a11d","tid":9862,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T17:50:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd8228a83220010d52bea20f895bc09da806d627","tid":9862,"uid":9869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T18:13:34.000Z","msg":"Wing Jai今年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6381c1948b5d04a2312617a8e107a3a548e40f","tid":9862,"uid":3373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T18:30:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳兆榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上場ABL入場睇，榮仔除咗一球block就無乜印象。<br />\n唔知艾利諾獨定係賽前部署，好多戰術都係做比艾利諾打。阿GA復出係開心，但唔鐘意佢輸左波賽後都同Howard 笑笑口，畢竟係職業，勝利係你地職責，希望睇到你更在乎呢場比賽。再另外有球印象好深係守二三聯防，人地擺明射你45度，有球潘志豪唔知咩事縮左入罰球線，籃底張文平見唔對路都即刻撲出去 呢球反映到潘有啲心散，亦睇到張文平既智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce59a36967b810e4709d8977f5337efcf9cb703","tid":9862,"uid":67942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T19:31:51.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e0839dd4315c0c1b182cf1a94bd2a5857730f2bd","tid":9862,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T20:12:35.000Z","msg":"完全無人理，好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf7bad5e45b9f1c5e8c2061554e0d1367c8e182","tid":9862,"uid":66314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:15:42.000Z","msg":"依家先見到呢個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽晚去唔去睇abl"}]}